    "headline": "Invesco Ltd. Announces February 28, 2026 Assets Under Management",
    "summary": "Invesco Ltd. (NYSE: IVZ)1, a leading global asset management firm announced today preliminary month-end assets under management (AUM) of $2,257.7 billion, an increase of 1.2% versus previous month-end. The firm delivered net long-term inflows of $4.7 billion in the month. Money market net inflows were $13.5 billion. AUM was positively impacted by favorable market returns which increased AUM by $9 billion. FX decreased AUM by $1.1 billion. Preliminary average total AUM for the quarter through Feb",
